If [F:BPS]BPSNUM<>[F:SCO]BPRNUM
  Read [BPS] BPS0=[F:SCO]BPRNUM : If fstat Raz [F:BPS] : Endif
Endif
If [F:MVS]BPSRSK<>[F:BPS]BPSRSK  | [F:MVS]CPY<>GSOCIETE    |
&  [F:MVS]BPSNUM<>[F:SCO]BPRNUM | [F:MVS]CUR<>GCUR
  Read [MVS] MVS0=[F:BPS]BPSRSK;GSOCIETE;[F:SCO]BPRNUM;GCUR
